  "title": "HuggingFace 发布超 200 页「实战指南」，从决策到落地「手把手」教你训练大模型",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651000674&idx=2&sn=39634c52d4546d5bb9ab0f8b039f1252",
  "date": "2025-11-09 11:47:00",
